Package: l1tfplus
Title: Fits piecewise linear trend based on L1 regularisation and extracts
    features
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Roy","Wilson",email="roy.wilson@hp.com",role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package contains functions that enhance the L1 regularised
    piecewise linear trend package l1tf.  The main function fits the model on a
    given vector and then returns a list that contains a summary of the
    attributes of each segment
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Imports:
    l1tf,
    zoo
